'''{{lang|en|Media Player Classic Home Cinema}}'''，簡稱'''{{lang|en|MPC-HC}}'''，是一款簡潔的媒體播放器，[[Media_Player_Classic|Media Player Classic]] 的後續版本，有[[x86|32位元]]和[[x64|64位元]]版本。2017年7月16日，原作者XhmikosR在發佈1.7.13版後宣佈由於開發者的流失，如沒有其他開發者加入的話，項目將會正式終結<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://mpc-hc.org/2017/07/16/1.7.13-released-and-farewell/ |title = v1.7.13 is released and farewell |author = XhmikosR |date = 2017-07-16 |publisher = MPC-HC |language = en |accessdate = 2017-07-16 |quote =  |archive-date = 2017-07-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170716185950/https://mpc-hc.org/2017/07/16/1.7.13-released-and-farewell/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。後續由 clsid2 接替更新1.7.13後版本<ref>{{Citation|title=Media Player Classic. Contribute to clsid2/mpc-hc development by creating an account on GitHub|url=https://github.com/clsid2/mpc-hc|date=2019-02-06|accessdate=2019-02-07|last=clsid2|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230020620/https://github.com/clsid2/mpc-hc/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

